0.3.0 Released June 12, 2013
----------------------------

- Allow 'output' configuration entry to set the output directory
- Write bundle parents into directories with index.html
- Only look for a single content plugin to process content data
- Bundle meta data 'url' can override the URL linked to for the bundle
- html5boilerplate pack uses domain in script and style links, for prefixes
- Bundle.get_collection(name) finds a collection a bundle is a member of
- Bundle.get_collections() finds all collections a bundle is a member of
- sortbundles template filter can take multiple comma-separated fields
- Linking between rst content supports anchors in references
- Sorting bundles by date and datetime objects is handled properly
